# 📁 Project Management Templates

This repository contains a complete collection of **editable Excel templates** for project management, organized by functional area. These templates are designed to help professionals with planning, tracking, risk analysis, budgeting, and resource management to improve **efficiency, clarity, and collaboration** across any type of project.

---

## 🎯 What's in this repository?

Templates are grouped into **four major categories** for easy navigation and practical use:

---

### 🟦 PLANNING & GENERAL CONTROL

| Template                        | Description                                                                 |
|--------------------------------|-----------------------------------------------------------------------------|
| Action Plan                  | Task plan with owners, deadlines, and statuses.                            |
| Project Charter                | Project initiation document with objectives, scope, and resources.         |
| Project Proposal Cost          | Cost proposal for early-stage project estimation.                          |
| Project Resource Plan          | Initial planning for human and material resources.                         |
| Project Status Report          | Periodic project update report.                                            |
| Project Timeline               | Visual timeline with milestones and phases.                                |
| PMO Budget Template            | Budget overview for the Project Management Office.                         |
| PMO Financial Statement        | Financial summary at PMO level.                                            |
| PMO Multiple Project Template  | File to manage multiple projects in one place.                             |

---

### 🟩 MONITORING & TRACKING

| Template                   | Description                                                               |
|---------------------------|---------------------------------------------------------------------------|
| Project Dashboard       | KPI dashboard with visual summaries.                                      |
| 🗓Project Calendar        | Editable calendar for project milestones.                                 |
| Task Manager              | Task assignment and progress control.                                     |
| Task Tracker Template     | Task tracking with priorities and due dates.                              |
| Issue Tracker             | Log for tracking issues and resolution.                                   |
| Risk Register             | Risk matrix with impact assessment and mitigation strategies.              |
| Stakeholder Analysis      | Mapping of key stakeholders by influence and interest.                     |
| Status Register           | Record of project statuses and updates.                                    |
| Kanban Board           | Visual workflow with task columns (To Do, In Progress, Done).             |
| Punch List                | Final to-do list before project closeout.                                  |

---

### 🟨 BUDGET & COST MANAGEMENT

| Template                    | Description                                                               |
|----------------------------|----------------------------------------------------------------------------|
| Annual Financial Report    | Yearly financial report for project or PMO.                                |
| Change Log Template        | Log of change requests and approvals.                                      |
| Cost Benefit Analysis      | Comparison of costs and expected benefits.                                 |
| Detailed Costed Workplan   | Workplan with itemized cost estimation.                                    |
| Gap Analysis               | Identification of gaps between current and desired states.                 |
| Production Scheduling      | Planning of production phases and schedules.                               |
| Project Budget Review      | Review and adjustments to the original budget.                             |
| Project Cost Control       | Real-time cost tracking tool.                                              |
| Project Cost Estimate      | Initial cost projection for planning purposes.                             |
| Project Cost Tracker       | Tracker comparing forecasted and actual costs.                             |
| Project Cost Trend Analysis| Trend analysis of cost progression.                                         |
| Estimate Template          | General-purpose template for early estimations.                            |

---

### 🟧 RESOURCES & RESPONSIBILITIES

| Template                      | Description                                                               |
|-------------------------------|----------------------------------------------------------------------------|
| RACI Template                 | Role matrix: Responsible, Accountable, Consulted, Informed.               |
| Resource Plan                | Resource allocation plan per task.                                        |
| Resource Planning Worksheet  | Spreadsheet to optimize resource distribution.                            |
| Timesheet                    | Log of hours worked by individual or team.                                |
| Work Schedule                | Weekly/monthly work schedule planner.                                     |
| To Do List                   | Simple task checklist for personal or team use.                           |
| WBS (Work Breakdown Structure)| Hierarchical breakdown of deliverables.                                   |

---

## 🛠️ How to use the templates

1. Download the template you need from the corresponding folder.
2. Open it in Excel or a compatible spreadsheet editor.
3. Customize the fields with your project information.
4. Save a copy for your reporting or tracking needs.

📝 Many templates include built-in formulas, visual icons, data validations, and conditional formatting.

---

## 📌 Requirements

- Microsoft Excel 2016 or newer
- (Optional) Google Sheets for online editing
- Recommended fonts: Segoe UI, Calibri, Arial

---

## 🤝 Contributions

Have a helpful, well-structured template to share?

1. Fork this repository.
2. Add your template to the relevant folder.
3. Submit a pull request with a short description of your addition.

---

## 📩 Need help?

You can open an [issue](https://github.com/Sladela/project-management-templates/issues) if:

- You have questions about any template
- You find a calculation error or formatting issue
- You want to suggest improvements

